Package: eflINLA
Type: Package
Title: Utilities used with INLA by FL
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Frank Lefever
Maintainer: Frank Lefever <flefebvre01@hotmail.com>
Description: Utilities to use with the INLA package.
    Different tools to create summaries, plots with the INLA package. Inspired
    by the `brinla` package but using the tidyverse and with more documentation.
